{"tid":1599121,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格 4000萬+1鎊 VS 熱刺班主利維 5件波衫都送唔起","createTime":"2019-09-27T19:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T05:25:07.000Z","uid":42246,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6b29d62ee39c4e74d8664d172b09817a131120c8","tid":1599121,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T19:59:01.000Z","msg":"邊個小家d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日，薩格勒布戴拿模的總監Zdravko Mamic憶述當年與熱刺談判莫迪歷的轉會過程中的一件趣事，「利維是個首屈一指的談判者，他對一分一毫的敏感度難以言喻。<span style=\"color: red;\">正如當年我們完成莫迪歷轉會的細節時，我禮貌向他查問可否要5件印有莫迪歷名字的熱刺球衣，他未有拒絕。不過，在轉會的收據上列有轉會費，減去5件球衣的金額</span>，對我而言是十分神奇，但另一方面看見利維對球會的一分一毫亦十分着緊。」"},{"pid":"9580638604ec65861f09eb13f6004e579afa9830","tid":1599121,"uid":149607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:27:31.000Z","msg":"肉酸"},{"pid":"b014138b91d537130b9743fc98f75d06d0bd1698","tid":1599121,"uid":216279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:27:59.000Z","msg":"心態要調整<br />\n求幫推 或多或少有幫助<br />\n［反省］我發現好多人都搵唔到方向及定位 入嚟啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"618e3ba9e326b07b46057b1392bcdd45606f29d0","tid":1599121,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:47:44.000Z","msg":"小家到"},{"pid":"b39e7082edbdfc0f89af4d98bc16217a84f462d1","tid":1599121,"uid":5652,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:58:40.000Z","msg":"不過係一個簽到 一個簽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c3de8460636d9b115a73e73a20daff31bc76ba","tid":1599121,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484115199ffa2be4012033f4fe224eb6c439036d","tid":1599121,"u